query:
SELECT f.id, f.nome, t.id as turmaId, t.codigo, t.curso, e.id as eventoId
FROM formandos f
JOIN turmas t ON f.turmaId = t.id
LEFT JOIN eventos e ON e.turmaId = t.id
WHERE f.nome LIKE '%Aires%'
LIMIT 1
